  {{>head}}
  <body class="bg-blue-200">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    {{>header}}
    <section
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-screen bg-blue-200"
    >
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center mb-8">
        Get Emotional Support Anytime, Anywhere
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 text-center mb-8">
        Our emotional support bot is here to help you through your ups and
        downs. Whether you need someone to talk to or want to create comforting
        images, we've got you covered.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/Signup"
        class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
        >Get Started</a
      >
    </section>
    <section class="py-16 px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center mb-8">
        Features
      </h2>
      <div
        class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid gap-4 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <!-- Feature Box 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
            Basic Prompts Suggestions
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Our emotional support bot provides you with basic prompts
            suggestions to help you start a conversation. You can choose from
            questions such as "How are you feeling today?" or "What would you
            like to talk about?" to get started.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
            Payment Feature for Unlimited Features
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Our emotional support bot offers a premium version with unlimited
            features. With our payment feature, you can access up to 1000
            prompts and 50 image prompts per month. For those who need unlimited
            support, we offer a Premium+ version.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
            Login/Signup Feature
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            To access our premium and premium+ features, we offer a login/signup
            feature. Once you sign up, you can access all the features our
            emotional support bot has to offer.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="bg-blue-200 py-12 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row">
        <div class="flex-1 py-32">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
            Dall-e Integration
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
            In our premium version, we offer Dall-e integration where you can
            create comforting images of cats, puppies, cute things, and soft
            things. Our emotional support bot is here to help you feel better in
            every way possible.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <img
            src="./assests/cateimagebyOurAPI.png"
            alt=""
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-16 px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center mb-8">Pricing</h2>
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row">
        <!-- Free Version Box -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex-1 m-4 md:m-0 md:mr-4"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Free Version</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Get started with our free version which includes 5 prompts per
            month. Sign up now to receive emotional support from our bot.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/Signup"
            class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full mt-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out block md:inline-block"
            >Sign Up</a
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Premium Version Box -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex-1 m-4 md:m-0 md:mr-4"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Premium Version</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Upgrade to our premium version and get
            1000 prompts, 50 image prompts per month, and Dall-e
            integration for creating comforting images.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/Pricing"
            class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full mt-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out block md:inline-block"
            >Upgrade to Premium</a
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Premium+ Version Box -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex-1 m-4 md:m-0 md:ml-4"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Premium+ Version</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Get unlimited support from our emotional support bot along with all
            the features of our premium Version.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/Pricing"
            class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full mt-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out block md:inline-block"
            >Upgrade to Premium+</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
